description	"212th Strike Ops. Clone Trooper

^2Weaponry:
- DC-15 Clone Pistol (1)
- DC-15S Carbine (3)

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcements (1)
- Stamina	(2)
- Assemble
- Ammo (2)

The Clone Trooper, pride of the Republic.  Cloned using the genetic template of Jango Fett, these mass produced troopers were naturally talented in combat. A handful of 212th, some of the highly skilled clone troopers, were able to board the Invisible Hand and assist in Anakin and Obi-Wan's rescue mission.
"